## Patterns Discovered

### Metrics Architecture
- Metrics endpoint runs in background thread (non-blocking)
- Port configurable via METRICS_PORT env var (default 8000)
- Prometheus text format v0.0.4 served at `/metrics`
- All metrics use `crawl4ai_` prefix consistently

### Sentry Integration
- Located in `utils/sentry.py`
- Initialized via `init_sentry()` function
- Uses SENTRY_DSN env var
- Adds contextual tags: job_id, scraper_name, extraction_mode, request_url

### Error Types in Metrics
From metrics.py ErrorType enum:
- network_error
- timeout
- rate_limit
- anti_bot_detected
- parse_error
- validation_error
- llm_error
- unknown

### Extraction Modes
- llm_free: DOM parsing, no AI cost
- llm: AI extraction with cost tracking
- auto: Automatic selection based on page complexity

